data.description: Exceptional views of country living with all the convenience of living in town. Modern 3-bedroom ranch on spacious half acre lot.  Enjoy the recently renovated kitchen with new appliances, backsplash, and counters.  Plenty of space to make the finished lower level your very own office, den, or game room.  The dining area leads to the sliding glass door into the spacious fenced backyard with a large deck and patio to appreciate the beautiful view.  Additional updates include the tub, tile, paint, cabinets, flooring, light fixtures, and heated garage!
